{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Allow cancelled passports to be reactivated if found within reasonable timeframe",
        "additional_details": "When a UK passport is reported lost, it is immediately cancelled, even if later found, forcing holders to pay \u00a394.50 unnecessarily. Allowing reactivation within a few hours or a day, with strict security checks, would save money, reduce hassle, and be fair, while keeping border security intact.",
        "background": "Once a UK passport is reported lost, it is cancelled and cannot be used, even if later found. We ask the Government to allow reactivation within a reasonable timeframe, with security checks.",
